
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Fracture of sternum' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And '16.3.1: Manubrium' radio button is enabled
And '16.3.2: Body' radio button is enabled
And '16.3.3: Xiphoid process' radio button is enabled
And '16.3: Sternal fracture, not further defined' radio button is enabled


When I select '16.3.1: Manubrium' radio button
Then '1A: Transverse fracture' radio button is enabled
And '1B: Oblique fracture' radio button is enabled
And '1C: Multifragmentary fracture' radio button is enabled

When I select '16.3.2: Body' radio button
Then '2A: Transverse fracture' radio button is enabled
And '2B: Oblique fracture' radio button is enabled
And '2C: Multifragmentary fracture' radio button is enabled

When I select '16.3.3: Xiphoid process' radio button
Then '3A: Transverse fracture' radio button is enabled
And '3B: Oblique fracture' radio button is enabled
And '3C: Multifragmentary fracture' radio button is enabled

When I select '16.3: Sternal fracture, not further defined' radio button
Then 'Fracture older, remodeled' checkbox is enabled
